snippet.title: Diluvian Ultra Chapter One - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Chapter One of Diluvian Ultra will be available on PC via Steam, GOG, and Epic Games Store on September 28, 2023. Check out the action-packed trailer for Diluvian Ultra to see gameplay, enemies, and more from this retro-inspired first-person shooter game.


In Diluvian Ultra, become an immortal warrior-prince, pick up your blood-sword and paint the corridors of your tomb-ship red with the blood of your enemies, using an upgradeable arsenal of Tech weapons as well as grotesque, living Organic armaments and combine Armor and Lethal damage types to dispatch your foes.
